        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine domini Dei et hominis. Anno incarnationis eiusdem millesimo
                        centesimo vigesimo secundo, XIll kalendas decembris, indicione XVma. Constat
                        nos <persName ref="#people/3552"
                            key="#marriage #parentOf #Lombard #Villas #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio #Witness"
                            >Helicam</persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">relictam</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3554" key="#marriage #Lombard">Alberti</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/4126">Bahonę</placeName> et <persName
                            ref="#people/3553"
                            key="#childOf #Villas #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio #Witness"
                            >Mainfredum</persName>, <rs key="#parentOf">matrem</rs> et <rs
                            key="#childOf #Lombard #mundualdusOf">filium</rs>, qui professi sumus
                        nos lege vivere <rs key="#Lombard">Longobardorum</rs>, ipso filio ac <rs
                            key="#mundualdusOf">mundoaldo</rs> meo michi consentiente et
                        auctoritatem suam interponente, accepisse a te <persName ref="#people/3550"
                            key="#Priors #Missus #Monasteries">Rodulpho</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priore</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Priors #Missus #Villas #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Forests #Rivers #Canals #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fisheries #Mills #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Venditio"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2075">Sancti Cypriani</orgName> quod in
                            <placeName key="#Monasteries #Curtes" ref="#places/914"
                            >Venetia</placeName> situm est sicut in presentia <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs> manifesti sumus quod accępimus <rs key="#Price">inter
                            argentum et aliam rem valentem libras ducentas monetę Venetialis</rs>
                        finitum precium sicut inter nos convenit, nominative pro duabus portionibus
                        totius rei immobilis quam Albertus de Bahone habebat et tenebat <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure proprietario</rs> tempore
                        mortis suę quamque nos habemus et possidemus sive per successionem sive
                        quocumque alio modo in <orgName key="#Dioecesis" ref="#juridical_persons/65"
                                ><rs key="#Dioecesis">episcopatu</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Dioecesis #Villas" ref="#places/41"
                                >Patavino</placeName></orgName>, in <geogName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Villas #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Legumes #Wine #Canals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#estates/2072"><rs key="#Villas">villa</rs> quaes dicitur
                                <placeName ref="#places/4127" key="#Villas">Castellum de
                                Brenta</placeName></geogName>, tam infra ipsam villam quamque de
                        foris in eius finibus ac territoriis, cum <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sediminibus</rs> seu <rs key="#Cereals">terris
                            arabilibus</rs>, vigris, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Legumes">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>,
                            <rs key="#Hay/fodder #Animals">pascuis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">silvis ac stellareis</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivis</rs>, rupinis ac <rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                            >paludibus</rs>, <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus</rs>, cultis
                        et incultis, divisis et indivisis, una cum finibus et tenninibus,
                        accessionibus et <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">usibus
                            aquarum</rs>, <rs key="#Canals">aquarumque ductibus</rs>, cum omni iure
                        ac iacentiis et pertinentiis suis in integrum. Quasautem suprascriptas duas
                        portiones totius proprietatis quam ut dictum est Albertus de Bahone habuit
                        in prenominato loco qui dicitur Castellum de Brenta ab hac die tibi cui
                        supra Rodulpho ac monasterio Sancti Cypriani per te priorem et <rs
                            key="#Missus">missum</rs> eius nos qui supra mater et filius pro iam
                        dicto precio vendimus, tradimus et mancipamus, nulli alii venditas, donatas,
                        alienatas vel traditas nisi tibi ac tuo monasterio, ut facias exinde a
                        presenti die tu et successores tui vel cui pars prefati monasterii dederit
                        iure ac proprietario nomine quicquid volueritis sine omni nostra et heredum
                        nostroum contradictione. Quidem et spondemus atque promittimus nos ac
                        nostros heredes tibi cui supra tuisque successoribus et tuo monasterio aut
                        cui pars eiusdem rnonasterii dederit prefatam venditionem qualiter superius
                        legitur in integrum ab omni homine defensare. Quod si defendere non
                        potuerimus aut si vobis exinde aliquid per quodvis ingenium extorquere
                        presumpserimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> eandem venditionem ut
                        prelegitur vobis restituemus sicut pro tempore fuerit meliorata aut valuerit
                        sub estimatione in consimili loco. Et ne nobis liceat ullo tempore nolle
                        quod voluimus id quod a nobis semel factum vel conscriptum est
                        inviolabiliter conservare promittimus, quia nichil nobis ex ipso precio
                        deberi diximus. Actum in Venetia, in <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <persName key="#Curtes"><name ref="Dominicus/Barbi">Dominici
                            Barbi</name></persName> feliciter. Signa ++ manuum predictorum matris et
                        filii qui hanc <rs key="#Venditio">cartulam venditionis</rs> fieri
                        rogaverunt. Rogati autem sunt testes: <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Causidicus #Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Ardericus"
                                >Ardericus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidici</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Causidicus #Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Raginaldus de Transelgardo">Rainaldus</name></persName> de
                        Transelgardo, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Bernardus de Bellone">Bernardus</name></persName> de Bellone,
                            <persName key="#Notary #Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Heinricus de Montegalda">Heinricus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/4128"
                            >Montegalda</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio #siblingOf"
                                ><name ref="Ermannus">Hermannus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs>
                        <persName key="#siblingOf"><name ref="Iohannis/Sicherii">Iohannis
                                Sicherii</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Bonifacius de Vigoncia">Bonefacius</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/4129">Vigoncia</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Venditio"><name ref="Liutulfus de Adeste"
                                >Litulphus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4130"
                            >Adeste</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Robertus de Capitesilvę">Robertus</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/4131">Capitesilvę</placeName> et alii. (M)
                            <persName key="#Causidicus #Tabellio #Writer #Venditio"><name
                                ref="Ionas/causidicus et tabellio">Ionas</name></persName>
                        causidicus necnonque <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> dictus huius
                        contractus <rs key="#Writer">conscripsi</rs> pacta rogatus. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
